snippet.title: SteadyGang【有红包拿】Official MV - 2026年用最夸张的方式回家的年歌
snippet.description:
Steady Gang今年用最大阵仗，横跨海陆空方式都要回家过年！
就算塞车都不能阻止我们回乡过年！

=====

《有红包拿》歌词

有红包拿 有红包拿 有红包拿

要买新年衣 黑的不能拿
穿到Ang Ang像 新年的 super star
红包肉干 这个那个呢个拿
准备回家 背后给我放烟花

新年集合  猛踩油门 没人能阻挡我返乡回城
highway车马填门 我攻破红城 一路上我 手起刀落 我手起刀落

我站在PG 一路杀到JB 红包大大封 裝滿口袋裡
准备派到你家 天空给我爆炸  闪电打雷  欢迎我们回家
 (红包我那个呢个拿)

新年福气 不要独孤一个拿
敲锣鼓咚 不要独孤一个打
红包我那个呢个拿
舞狮舞龙 一起隆咚锵咚锵

新年祝福 不要独孤一个拿
麻将台座 不要独孤一个打
肉干我那个呢个拿
有红包拿 一起huat到爆炸

爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 红包包大大
红包我那个呢个拿 舞狮舞龙 一起隆咚锵咚锵

肉干我那个呢个拿 整个大马 一起huat到爆炸

这个那个呢个一起 skrrrr
那个呢个这个跟我 burrrr
赛车我坐helicopter (still jam?)
我再坐船 回 East Malaysia

新年回家气势不能 怂 怂
给爸妈的红包就要 厚 厚
喇叭开最大给我 BOOM BOOM
这个新年我就是要 Ong Ong
（红包我那个呢个拿）

新年福气 不要独孤一个拿
敲锣鼓咚 不要独孤一个打

红包我那个呢个拿 舞狮舞龙 一起隆咚锵咚锵
爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 红包包大大
肉干我那个呢个拿 整个大马 一起huat到爆炸

爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 红包包大大
包给爸妈爸妈 包给爸爸妈妈 包给干爸干妈 包给干爸妈

Wow 爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 红包包大大
红包我拿 那个呢个拿 那个呢个拿啊~~

爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 爸妈爸妈 马上就到家
肉干我那个呢个拿 整个大马 一起huat到爆炸

snippet.title: Anime “Dragon Ball Super: Beerus” | SUPER Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Series Premieres in Fall of 2026!
The anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus in Fall 2026!

#dragonball #dragonballsuper

◾️INTRODUCTION
The globally beloved manga DRAGON BALL by Akira Toriyama continues to captivate fans through a wide range of media—from TV animation, movies, games, and merchandising—standing as a top-ranked title with extraordinary worldwide popularity. 
Now, in 2026, the anime Dragon Ball Super, original work, story, and character design by Akira Toriyama, is set to begin anew as Dragon Ball Super: Beerus! This ENHANCED edition introduces a large volume of newly added and redrawn cuts, as well as a reconstructed narrative. With cutting-edge visual expression, the series delivers even more immersive battle scenes and a more faithful representation of the original manga—bringing an ENHANCED edition to life like never before.

Several years have passed since the fierce battle against Majin Buu, and Earth has finally regained a brief moment of peace. At the same time, Beerus, the God of Destruction, awakens from his long, deep sleep. Even Kai and Supreme Kai, aware of Beerus’s overwhelming power to destroy entire planets, watch his awakening with great fear… Meanwhile, Beerus hears rumors of a Saiyan who defeated Frieza—and suddenly appears before Goku.
Targeted by Beerus, the strongest being in the universe, Earth is in grave danger. Thus begins an Earth-shattering cosmic battle between the God of Destruction and Goku and his allies—a conflict that will shake the entire universe.

Original Work, Story & Character Design: Akira Toriyama

snippet.title: Izin Sayang - Jasmin Sofea ft AXA Band (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Lagu ini mengangkat kisah penderitaan seorang isteri yang setia apabila kepercayaan dan cinta yang dibina bersama suami akhirnya musnah akibat kecurangan. Terperangkap antara kenangan manis perkahwinan dan realiti pahit pengkhianatan, watak ini melalui luka yang senyap namun mendalam. Dengan nada pilu dan sarat emosi, karya ini menzahirkan kekuatan seorang wanita yang terpaksa membuat pilihan sukar sama ada terus bertahan demi cinta yang pernah mekar atau melepaskan segalanya demi maruah serta ketenangan jiwa. Lagu ini ditutup dengan refleksi menyentuh hati tentang nilai kejujuran dan makna sebenar kesetiaan dalam sebuah perkahwinan.

Lagu ini merupakan hasil ciptaan Jasmin Sofea bersama AXA Band. Jasmin Sofea dikenali sebagai seorang pempengaruh media sosial yang disegani bukan sahaja kerana bakat dan pengaruhnya malah kerana imej positif yang dibawa tanpa sebarang kontroversi. Keperibadiannya yang penyayang turut diperkukuhkan dengan kehadiran ibunya Ibu Shu yang sering memberikan dorongan serta nilai murni untuk dijadikan teladan di media sosial.

Sementara itu AXA Band merupakan antara kumpulan muzik yang sedang meningkat naik dalam industri tempatan. Single sulung mereka Cinta Matiku telah meninggalkan kesan mendalam kepada pendengar menerusi lirik yang menyentuh perasaan dan mesej kesetiaan sekali gus mengajak pendengar untuk menghargai serta mempertahankan cinta sejati hingga ke akhir hayat.

*Stream 'Izin Sayang’ on all digital streaming platforms:* https://bfan.link/izin-sayang

snippet.title: Supergirl | Blast Off :30
snippet.description:
It’s called making an entrance. #Supergirl lands in theaters and IMAX June 26.

“Supergirl,” DC Studios’ newest feature film to hit the big screen, will be in theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures, starring Milly Alcock in the dual role of Supergirl/Kara Zor-El. Craig Gillespie directs the film from a screenplay by Ana Nogueira.

When an unexpected and ruthless adversary strikes too close to home, Kara Zor-El, aka Supergirl, reluctantly joins forces with an unlikely companion on an epic, interstellar journey of vengeance and justice.

Alcock stars alongside Matthias Schoenaerts, Eve Ridley, David Krumholtz, Emily Beecham, and Jason Momoa. DC Studios heads Peter Safran and James Gunn are producing the film, which is based on characters from DC, Supergirl based on characters created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film is executive produced by Nigel Gostelow, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars P. Winther. Behind the camera, Gillespie is joined by director of photography Rob Hardy, production designer Neil Lamont, editor Tatiana S. Riegel, costume designer Anna B. Sheppard, Visual Effects Supervisor Geoffrey Baumann, and composer Ramin Djawadi.

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment Production, The Safran Company Production, A Film by Craig Gillespie, “Supergirl,” which will be in theaters and IMAX® across North America on June 26, 2026, and internationally beginning 24 June 2026, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: 《2026年馬年新年歌 》 韓曉噯HANXIIAOAII   【小妹祝你發大財! 】OFFICIAL CNY MUSIC VIDEO
snippet.description:
《小妹祝你發大財》以歡快旋律為起點,
融合節慶氛圍與當代流行元素,
韓曉噯的這首新年單曲不只傳遞祝福,
更是一份真摯的家族紀念與文化傳承。

因家人來自 “Kampung”(鄉村),平日對她的事業難以參與理解,
韓曉噯特別邀請全家入鏡 MV,讓這次創作成為溫暖的團聚行動。

歌中融入親切的 福建話 對白,既是她作為福建人對自身文化的致敬與傳承,
也令歌曲更貼近家族的情感根源。
自稱 “小妹」,唱出 「一家團圓笑口常開」、「莫講我Bojio你,趕緊來拜年」 等歌詞,
正是她對家人隨意生活的擁抱－用一首歌,留住相伴的鄉音與時光。

全曲在熱鬧編曲中鋪陳細膩心意,
從 “拿Angpow誰叫我還是單身” 的幽默,
到 “願你平安每一天」的叮嚷,
再到 「Huat到天明」 的暢想,
都讓傳統祝福多了年輕的生命力。

這不僅是一首新年歌,
更是韓曉噯送給家人的音樂合照──讓工作成為相聚的理由,
讓歌聲成為親情的延續,
也讓熟悉的方言在節奏中代代相傳。

Presented By
Tropicana 
https://www.facebook.com/tropicanacorp
https://www.instagram.com/tropicanacorpbhd/

Co-sponsor By 
Cnc 礼篮 
https://www.instagram.com/cnc_worldwide_hamper/

Kafen 
https://www.facebook.com/kafenmalaysia.official
https://www.instagram.com/kafenmalaysiaofficial/

QIPAO & SONGKET By
https://www.instagram.com/peonysin_official/
